title: Carbs and Ratings
description: This project focuses on analyzing the relationship between the amount of carbohydrates in a recipe and the rating of the recipe.

title: Expository Visualization of Food
description: This project focuses on creating a graph to showcase a trend in processing levels in food bought at grocery stores.

title: Persuasive and Deceptive Visualization of Populations
description: This project focuses on creating a graph showcasing youth populations growth and decline.

title: Bikewatching
description: This project presents an interactive map visualization of bike traffic in and around Boston. It shows how bike traffic changes throughout the day.

title: Water Vapor Visualizations
description: This project focuses on how the mean brightness temperature of water vapor changes over the year of 2025.
